summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2938, for the improvement of West Lander Street, from Whatcom Avenue to East Waterway, all in the City of Seattle, by filling; planking and replanking the same, and providing for the necessary surface drainage; under Ordinance No. 35484 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
